"Set the space in centimeters between two points on an horizontal line on the "
"grid. Default is 0.5 centimeter."
msgstr ""
"Indstiller afstanden i centimeter mellem to punkter på en vandret linje i "
"gitteret. Standardværdien er 5 centimeter."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: options.docbook:137
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Vertical alignment:"
