msgstr "Lodret justering:"

#. Tag: para
#: options.docbook:138
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Set the space in centimeters between two points on a vertical line on the "
"grid. Default is 0.5 centimeter."
msgstr ""
"Indstiller afstanden i centimeter mellem to punkter på en lodret linje i "
"gitteret. Standardværdien er 5 centimeter."

